<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=1780&amp;p=9196#p9196"><![CDATA[
The .skin files have changed significantly to account for new features. The .skin7 are even more different because they need to support additional graphical elements for the Windows 7 style.<br /><br />I would recommend you start from one of the existing skins, particularly if you mostly changed the bitmaps. Otherwise you may end up with hard to track bugs.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2">Ivo</a> — Sat Nov 30, 2013 10:06 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
